    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>Is this resume AI-generated?</h3>
    <p>No — every word and layout was crafted by Suzanne Church. BBLite_SUZE is a guide she designed to enhance clarity and engagement.</p>

    <h3>Can I view a traditional resume?</h3>
    <p>Yes — the modular resume is available in PDF format upon request or via Dropbox link.</p>

    <h3>What is Business Buddy Lite?</h3>
    <p>BBLite_SUZE is a branded assistant created by Suzanne to guide viewers through her resume experience. It’s not a chatbot — it’s a storytelling layer.</p>

    <h3>How does this system reflect Suzanne’s skills?</h3>
    <p>It showcases her strengths in modular system design, user-centric logic, and strategic branding — all wrapped in a creative, interactive format.</p>

    <h3>Can this system be adapted for other roles?</h3>
    <p>Absolutely. Persona modes like Executive, Programmer, and Gamer are built into the system’s logic and can be toggled for tailored experiences.</p>
